<body>
    <header>
        <h1>My Favorite Recipe: Arabic Shawarma</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>1 pack Arabic Bread</li>
            <li>1 pc Lettuce</li>
            <li>1 liter Garlic Sauce</li>
            <li>1 pack French Fries</li>
            <li>1 gram Chicken Shawarma</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Slice the the Shawarma chicken into a medium size diced.</li>
            <li>Get your arabic bread and put the diced Shawarma Chicken in.</li>
            <li>Put the Garlic Sauce, French Fries, and Lettuce in.</li>
            <li>Wrap it and toast on a pan.</li>
            <li>Top and bottom should be light brown after that just slice it at the middle wallah Arabic Shawarma.</li>
        </ol>
    </main>
